Package: dfrtopics
Title: Tools for exploring topic models of text
Description: This package provides tools for exploring topic models created by MALLET, with specialized functions for handling JSTOR Data for Research data.
Version: 0.2.1
Author: Andrew Goldstone <andrew.goldstone@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Andrew Goldstone <andrew.goldstone@gmail.com>
